These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-3-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, milk, mirinda, tea
House: wooden, victorian, modern, ranch-style
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rowing, skateboarding, rugby, sailing
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, ship, tram, van
 1. the victorian house is on the left or right of the person driving the ship##3
 2. the person drinking milk is the ranch-style house##1
 3. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
 5. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the modern house is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rowing##3
 7. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
 8. the person drinking tea is on the right of the modern house##1
 9. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far left##1
10. the person who's sport is rugby is on the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
11. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2      |      3      |   4   |
| Beverage    | mirinda   | milk       | almond-milk | tea   |
| House        | victorian    | ranch-style  | modern      | wooden |
| Sport         | sailing      | skateboarding | rugby         | rowing   |
| Transport   | quad-bike | ship       | tram        | van   |

