.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-3-2::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, electrician, photographer, police-officer
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, february, november, october
City: san-francisco, berlin, new-york, liverpool
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, roller, tram, trike
1. the person traveling to new-york is on the left of the person traveling to berlin##1
2. the electrician is the person who's birthday is in september##1
3. the person driving the tram is the photographer##1
4. the bartender is between the person who's birthday is in february and the person driving the car##2
5. the person driving the car is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
6. the person traveling to liverpool is the person driving the trike##1
7. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the far right##1
8. the person driving the car is on the far left or far right##3
9. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |       3        |      4       |
| Job           | electrician | bartender | police-officer | photographer |
| Birthday   | september  | november | february         | october      |
| City         | new-york      | berlin    | liverpool         | san-francisco   |
| Transport     | car         | roller    | trike          | tram         |

