.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-3-3::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, bluemaster, oliveros, game
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, gospel, indie, rock
4 different pets are kept: cat, dog, hedgehog, turtle
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, fanta, cola, coffee
 1. the fan of indie is the oliveros-smoker##1
 2. the fan of folk is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the game-smoker is on the left or right of the person drinking cola##3
 4. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
 5. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the fan of rock##1
 6. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the person drinking coffee##3
 7. the fan of folk is on the left of the person drinking water##1
 8. the owner of the cat is between the person drinking cola and the fan of gospel##2
 9. the game-smoker is on the left of the blend-smoker##1
10. the bluemaster-smoker is on the left or right of the game-smoker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |     4      |
| Cigar          | bluemaster | game  | blend | oliveros      |
| Music-Genre   | folk       | rock    | gospel      | indie      |
| Pet           | turtle     | cat     | dog         | hedgehog   |
| Beverage         | cola | water | fanta     | coffee |

