.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-3-5::.
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, argentine, spanish, indian
There 4 different types of food: carrot, kiwi, pineapple, zucchini
4 different games are played: billiard, bridge, go, monopoly
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, basketball, cycling, ice-hockey
 1. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left or right of the person eating kiwi##3
 2. the person eating zucchini is on the left or right of the person eating carrot##3
 3. the canadian is on the left of the person eating pineapple##1
 4. the person eating zucchini is on the right of the person eating carrot##1
 5. the indian is on the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 6. the indian is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person playing billiard is on the left or right of the person eating zucchini##3
 8. the spanish is on the left of the person eating kiwi##1
 9. the person eating pineapple is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
10. the person playing monopoly is between the canadian and the person playing go##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |     3     |     4      |
| Nationality      | indian | canadian | spanish     | argentine       |
| Food          | carrot   | zucchini    | pineapple | kiwi       |
| Game   | billiard     | bridge       | monopoly    | go     |
