 8. the dutch is the person driving the snowmobile##1
 9. the french is on the left or right of the person eating watermelon##3
10. the person who growsrose is on the far right##1
11. the german is the person eating watermelon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |   2    |      3      |     4      |
