.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-3-19::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: rose, dahlia, poppy, lily
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, documentary, martial-arts, zombie
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, dubstep, metal, r&b
The people have 4 different jobs:  pilot, firefighter, entrepreneur, fisherman
 1. the fan of r&b is on the right of the pilot##1
 2. the person watching animation movies is the person who growsdahlia##1
 3. the fisherman is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person who growspoppy is on the left or right of the person who growslily##3
 5. the person who growslily is on the left of the fan of metal##1
 6. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left of the fisherman##1
 7. the person who growsrose is on the left of the firefighter##1
 8. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person who growslily##1
 9. the fisherman is the fan of r&b##1
10. the pilot is on the left or right of the fan of dubstep##3
11. the person watching zombie movies is the person who growsrose##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |      3       |     4     |
| Flower         | rose      | lily | poppy       | dahlia   |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie     | documentary | martial-arts | animation |
| Music-Genre   | ambient    | dubstep     | metal        | r&b       |
