.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-3-20::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, coffee, almond-milk, juice
The people have 4 different jobs:  analyst, dancer, mechanic, scientist
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, comedy, mystery, satire
There are 4 different nationalities: nigerian, thai, polish, japanese
 1. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far right##1
 2. the thai is on the right of the analyst##1
 3. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
 4. the dancer is between the polish and the thai##2
 5. the person watching adventure movies is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3
 6. the person watching adventure movies is between the dancer and the nigerian##2
 7. the person watching mystery movies is the scientist##1
 8. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person watching satire movies##1
 9. the person drinking almond-milk is the dancer##1
10. the person watching adventure movies is the mechanic##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |    3     |     4     |
| Beverage          | coffee | juice   | almond-milk   | soy-milk |
| Job           | analyst   | mechanic     | dancer   | scientist |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy    | adventure    | satire   | mystery   |
| Nationality         | nigerian    | thai | japanese | polish    |

 